{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-3", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "引燃草垛", "storyInfo": "眾人在村莊過夜，安置傷患，風笛和葦草談起了各自的過往。與此同時，阿赫茉妮意外聽到了葦草縱火的消息，她瞬間的反應被菲舍爾捕捉到了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，誰能想到逃難了這麼多天，居然還能安安穩穩坐在屋子裡吃上一頓熱飯菜。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個叫風笛的姑娘可真討人喜歡，剛剛我們還在誇她燉的菜好吃呢。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，這方面她確實不賴。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安置的事，你們商量得順利嗎？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都說定啦，趕不了路的人都可以留下，這兩天先借兩間倉庫躲一躲。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "逃難的人跟商隊打了一架，又沒真的搶到什麼東西，這種事太常見了，辦案的不會放在心上。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "過個幾天，廣播裡不報這些事情了，他們就不用躲了，可以動手建自己的房子了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，不過得了礦石病的那幾位，要住到離聚落遠一些的地方去。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的人很友善。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，是啊，我們當初逃出來的時候，一路上要是有人收留，也不至於變成現在這樣。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可這也不怪別人。以前聚落裡收留一兩批逃難的人，不是難事，只是現在大家都過得越來越糟糕了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你瞧塞爾蒙那小孩，要是有個地方能容下他們兄妹倆，她也不至於一直在各個聚落之間竄來竄去，到處惹事。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "像我們今天晚上可以在村子裡過夜，但塞爾蒙堅持自己在村外躲著，就是因為她在這裡搶過人家的牧獸，現在不好意思見那位老爺子......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉，當我沒說。讓她聽到了，又要說我不尊重她。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "晚上好......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，莫蘭？天都黑了，你怎麼過來的？趁現在還有燈，我帶你回去......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝，但我已經習慣摸黑走路了......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......請問，葦草在嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你找她？她獨自出門了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許葦草是有什麼煩心事吧......自從來了這裡，塞爾蒙就不肯和她說話。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，風笛去找她了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......或者換個說法，我們不如擔心葦草會嫌太吵吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g4_swamp_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "power": 10.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "jump", "xpos": 20.0, "power": 5.0, "times": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，抱歉！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒事。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，我沒想到這裡會有人，沒太仔細看。每次鐘聲一響，周圍就黑漆漆的，眼睛要過一會才能習慣。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好撞上的是你，換成其他人，可能就要被我撞倒了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我記得大家說好今天晚上不用放哨？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是......想在外面坐坐。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，乾草的味道很好聞，對吧。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......乾草？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，那邊的乾草垛。我好久沒聞到過這種氣味了，所以跑出來好好地聞一聞。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前我準備考軍校的時候，讀理論知識讀得頭疼了，只要在乾草垛上面躺一會，就感覺什麼都好了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然媽媽總說我這是在偷懶，不能因為想問題太辛苦就不去想......可是腦子裡有太多東西的話，就是挺累人的呀。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，把手給我一下？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#5$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#5$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來來來，一起躺嘛！就一會！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我不擅長想事情，也許幫不了你什麼，但乾草垛肯定能幫上你的！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#9"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hidehaystack", "volume": 0.9, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿——！", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風笛放鬆地躺在草垛上，輕輕哼著剛才從農戶那裡學來的歌謠。"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一陣溫潤的夜風吹過，葦草按照她的建議，深深地吸了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她聞到的不是乾草的香氣，而是潮濕的泥土與灰塵的味道。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想到自己竟然三年多沒有回過家了，總覺得好奇怪呀。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想呀，地等著我去翻土，麥子等著我去收割......一年不回家，就會把所有重要的事情全部錯過一遍。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連家裡寄來的信，我也要等下一次回羅德島的時候才能收到。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......很想家嗎？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然啦。你呢？你是小丘郡人嗎？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不是。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我以前也生活在和小丘郡差不多的城市裡......深紅色的磚牆，灰色的人行道，兩三層高的房子，花藤會長到窗戶外面。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......很懷念那段平靜的時光。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時候，家裡放著很多舊書，有的還是手抄本。我總是躲到書房裡，鎖上門，那樣就不用聽別人講話。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你家裡人很多所以太吵了？還是經常有人做客？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，還好。只是躲起來就可以避免很多麻煩。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從書房的窗戶，可以看到街道，看到父母結束一天的工作歸來。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果可以的話，我很想回到那裡。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，難道你說的地方已經......", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉......我是不是讓你更難過了？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係的，那是很早以前的事情了。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和小丘郡那些生活被毀掉的普通人，或者眼前這些背井離鄉的流民，也許沒有太大差別。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家可以在這裡安頓下來，重新搭起房子......可是，他們的家鄉在哪裡呢？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有那些，不得不走得更遠的人......他們又要逃到哪裡去呢？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......這些問題光靠一個人想是想不出答案的吧？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我也不是說你想這些就沒用啦！", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個人想不出答案的話，我們可以一起想。以前我遇到做不出的題目的時候，就老是去騷擾陳陳。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後來，我就總是拉著隊長......她們嘴上嫌我煩，可每一次都會陪我聊天，幫我解決難題的。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呢，你有什麼能說心裡話的人嗎？比如姐妹啊同學啊戰友啊之類......", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有......姐姐。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們關係不太好嗎？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，我不該這麼說。我不該......", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實塞爾蒙有一點說得對，你總是習慣性地說“不”。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是她有一點弄錯了，你呀，在說到自己的事的時候，才最喜歡說“不”，就好像......唔，我說不上來，就好像要費勁擺脫什麼似的。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有人對我說過類似的話。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸欸，是嗎？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......救了我，對我說，我不需要尋求死亡，也可以掙脫原本的命運。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Outcast呀，這確實很像她的語氣。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很後悔......後悔自己沒能努力再和她多說幾句話。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很想問問她，為什麼要救我？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她......從我身上看到了什麼？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我也不確定她會怎樣回答。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過葦草，在問她之前，你有問過自己嗎？你從你自己身上看到了什麼？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......自己？", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_hidehaystack", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6, "delay": 2.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，那邊有人出來了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個摸索的動作，應該是莫蘭......她夜裡看不見。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，那她怎麼自己跑出來了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫蘭小姐！有什麼我們能幫忙的嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，你先站在那裡等一下，我們過來啦。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g4_swamp_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......謝謝。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請問，葦草在哪裡？他們說，她出門了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "fadetime": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就在這裡。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉。請問，我可以跟你們一起走嗎？", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去哪裡都行。我還有些力氣，能幹活......也能戰鬥。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想......戰鬥？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。他們都說我活不久了，只能在哪個角落裡悄無聲息地死去。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我不想這樣。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“如果你作為塔拉人還想活下去，那就換工廠，接受更低的薪資”“如果你得了礦石病還想活下去，那就從這搬走，去感染者街區”......", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想再聽這種話了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草，我以前不會這樣想，但我遇見了你。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們告訴我，你也是感染者。是你說服了塞爾蒙和其他人，帶著我們走到了這裡。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......也和維恩一樣，相信我？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不要有壓力，我......我不想拖累你，拖累任何人。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想做點什麼，做什麼都好。像我這樣的人，已經不會再失去什麼了。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我能為其他塔拉人帶去一點什麼的話，我想去做。要是我的腿還能往前走的話，我想和你們一起走。", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#6$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得可以欸。葦草，不管怎麼樣，我們先一起走吧，好不好？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#8"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對紅髮瓦伊凡而言，這可能並不是一個需要葦草回答的問題。因為得到答案之前，她已經開始拉著葦草往前走了。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草回頭看了眼另一個人。她知道，莫蘭有夜盲症，到了晚上需要別人引路。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有什麼猶豫的時間，葦草向莫蘭伸出了手。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......一起走吧。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g5_noblehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮小姐，您可算來啦。我還以為今天沒機會見到您呢。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然是子爵大人舉辦的酒會，我又怎麼可能錯過？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然，當然。您可是特倫特侯爵的朋友，子爵大人的貴客。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了您介紹，我先前那單生意才能做成。我可一直想找機會謝謝您。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必那麼客氣，霍爾先生。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我既沒有貴族身份，名下也沒什麼產業，充其量只是個替大人物們奔走的信使罷了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（舉杯）", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位是......", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "市政部門的紅人，菲舍爾先生。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？先前我可沒怎麼聽說過他呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "菲舍爾先生調到這個郡也就是前不久的事情。像他這樣的年輕人，想要取得快速升遷的機會，總要格外努力一些。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵呵，誰又不是呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您過謙了。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，我聽幾位朋友說，最近大公爵們的軍隊調動都很頻繁，各大公爵領的核心城市均已戒嚴。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的消息一向靈通......能否透露一下，戰爭是不是近在眼前？", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報紙上都是這麼預測的吧？畢竟，公爵們的艦隊早就抵達倫蒂尼姆的城牆外啦。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並不是很關心薩卡茲，我是指大公爵之間......咳，我聽說，只是聽說而已。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最近有許多源石燃料流向特倫特郡。侯爵大人與開斯特公爵向來交好，可是特倫特郡與鐵公爵的領地毗鄰......", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，霍爾先生，跨城燃料交易可是必須經過審批的。想必您在市政部門一定有非常好的朋友，對吧？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈哈，都是為了生意而已。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮小姐，雖說您對戰爭的事情沒那麼感興趣，但是......您是從其他城市趕來的，對吧？", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好，您來時沒有遇到什麼麻煩，但返程時，還請繼續小心。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽說，移動城市外面的聚落很亂，時不時有叛亂份子出沒，前幾天還有人縱火。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼樣的叛亂份子值得您的關注？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說不上關注，類似的事件在那些鄉巴佬出沒的地方可多得是。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇怪的是那火......哈哈，也未必是真的，就當個鄉野奇聞說給您聽聽吧。", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "據目擊者說，那火和一般的火都不太一樣，威力跟爆炸似的，現場卻找不到源石爆炸物的痕跡，又極難撲滅......", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 200.0, "g": 200.0, "b": 200.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i03_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yFrom": 10.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 6.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 200.0, "g": 200.0, "b": 200.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特別的火。"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然很可能只是巧合，但類似的形容她很熟悉。"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道是......拉芙希妮？"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮很驚訝。"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“校官”的提醒的確喚醒了她心底的些許憂慮。自從那艘名為羅德島的艦船駛入維多利亞，她有一陣子沒能得到關於拉芙希妮的消息了。"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "毫無疑問，一定有人在幫羅德島隱匿行蹤，這家醫藥公司顯然比她最初設想的還要不簡單。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而這也意味著，身在羅德島的拉芙希妮並不會輕易地被維多利亞的其他勢力找到。"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是為什麼......為什麼拉芙希妮會離開那艘船？"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼她會出現在距離愛布拉娜這麼近的地方？"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i03_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在阿赫茉妮身後，一道視線投向了她。"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從阿赫茉妮踏入這個宴會廳開始，她的一舉一動自然都被關注著。"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可直到這一刻，那道視線才真正聚焦在了她身上。"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g5_noblehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_176"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮小姐？", "name": "熱情的商人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_176"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉......我剛剛在想晚上舞會的事。您覺得我佩戴什麼顏色的耳飾比較好？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......先生，您應當看過相關卷宗，還有我所有的報告了。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我建議我們立刻開始行動......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做得很好，年輕人。你品嚐過長桌上的威士忌夾心巧克力了嗎？", "name": "屏風後的女聲"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......貴安，開斯特公爵閣下。我沒有想到您會光臨這場宴會，還特意在這裡等待。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰能錯過這場盛大的宴會呢？僅僅是在隔間裡聽著室內樂隊的演奏，就令人心曠神怡。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真希望你也同樣享受。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......還有任務在身，不容鬆懈。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們所做的一切努力，終究是為了眾人能享受寧靜的生活。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情報人員雖然作為瞭望者，不得不在和平的年代裡也保持神經緊繃，但總會有獲得寧靜的那一天。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#7$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你的身體狀況如何？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......承蒙公爵閣下關照。您竟然關注到了我這樣一名普通情報人員的感染狀況。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用緊張，你沒有隱瞞什麼。如我所言，你做得很好。", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次任務結束後，作為獎賞，你是想要擢升，還是想要退出呢？", "name": "開斯特公爵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_726_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}